@model Starwars_API.Models.HomePageViewModel
<h2>Starwars Charatcter</h2>
<hr />
@using (Html.BeginForm("Index", "Home", FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "form" }))
{
    <div class="row form-group">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            @Html.TextBoxFor(textbox => textbox.SearchName, new { @class = "form-control" })
        </div>

        <div class="col-mid-3">
            <input type="submit" value="Search by Name" name="buttonType" class="btn btn-primary" />
        </div>
    </div>
    foreach (var person in Model.People)
    {
        <p class="card-header">
            @if (person.Name.ToLower() != "unknown")
            {
                <div> @Html.LabelFor(label => person.Name): <b>@person.Name</b></div>
            }
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="card-body">
            @if (person.BirthYear.ToLower() != "unknown")
            {
                <div> @Html.LabelFor(label => person.BirthYear): <b>@person.BirthYear</b></div>
            }
           



            @if (person.Mass.ToLower() != "unknown")
            {
                <div> @Html.LabelFor(label => person.Mass): <b>@person.Mass</b></div>
            }

            @if (person.EyeColor.ToLower() != "unknown")
            {
                <div> @Html.LabelFor(label => person.EyeColor): <b>@person.EyeColor</b></div>
            }

            @if (person.FilmCount.ToLower() != "unknown")
            {
                <div> @Html.LabelFor(label => person.FilmCount): <b>@person.FilmCount</b></div>
            }
        </p>
    }

    <div class="row">
        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Previous))
        {
            <div class="col-md-1">
                @Html.HiddenFor(hidden => hidden.Previous)
                <input type="submit" value="Previous" name="buttonType" class="btn btn-primary" />
            </div>
        }
        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Next))
        {
            <div class="col-md-1">
                @Html.HiddenFor(hidden => hidden.Next)
                <input type="submit" value="Next" name="buttonType" class="btn btn-primary" />
            </div>
        }
    </div>


    

}

}
